  section.slide#example
    h2 Example

    h3 Encryption
    pre
      |     P     I     E  message
      |  15(P)  8(I)  4(E) message
      | + 4(E)  0(A) 19(T) key
      | =19     8    23    message + key
      | =19(T)  8(I) 23(X) ciphertext (mod 26)
      |     T     I     X  ciphertext

    h3 Decryption
    pre
      |     T     I     X  ciphertext
      |  19(T)  8(I) 23(X) ciphertext
      | - 4(E)  0(A) 19(T) key
      | =15     8     4    ciphertext - key
      | =15(P)  8(I)  4(E) message (mod 26)
      |     P     I     E  message

    p This example uses modulo 26 addition and subtraction, while the
      Python example will use XOR (modulo 2).
